Package: rsnps
Title: Get 'SNP' ('Single-Nucleotide' 'Polymorphism') Data on the Web
Description: A programmatic interface to various 'SNP' 'datasets' on
        the web: 'OpenSNP' (<https://opensnp.org>), and 'NBCIs' 'dbSNP'
        database (<https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/projects/SNP/>).
        Functions are included for searching for 'NCBI'. For 'OpenSNP',
        functions are included for getting 'SNPs', and data for
        'genotypes', 'phenotypes', annotations, and bulk downloads of
        data by user.
Version: 0.6.1
